				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ho%C3%A0ng-H%E1%BA%A1c-l%C3%A2u/poem-12DeuGH-zr92vm-pHvDl_A">Đề Hoàng Hạc lâu - 題黃鶴樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/Thi%C3%AAn-H%C6%B0ng-tr%E1%BA%A5n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zfk8LWGL0mEgBMai1LRNPA">Thiên Hưng trấn phú - 天興鎮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/author-UlfffDmWp64stOugtjh9rQ">Nguyễn Bá Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BA%BFn-An/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-GL-mCqDi3fti6LhsXRKINw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ki%E1%BA%BFn-An/author-UyLRoCMAJQMpIMlO8d1-tQ">Kiến An</a>)<br></div>	</div>
